### Arabic

<span style="display: block; font-size: 180%; text-align: right;">ذَٰلِكَ بِأَنَّ ٱللَّهَ نَزَّلَ ٱلْكِتَـٰبَ بِٱلْحَقِّ ۗ وَإِنَّ ٱلَّذِينَ ٱخْتَلَفُوا۟ فِى ٱلْكِتَـٰبِ لَفِى شِقَاقٍۭ بَعِيدٍ</span>

### English

That is because Allah has revealed the Book in truth. And surely those who differ regarding it are totally engrossed in opposition.